'''史特林·桑德曼·奈特'''（'''{{lang|en|Sterling Sandmann Knight}}'''，{{bd|1989年|3月5日}}）為一名美國演員、歌手、詞曲作者、喜劇演員和音樂家。

== 早年生活 ==
史特林·奈特於1989年3月5日出生於南卡羅來納州[[希爾頓黑德島_(南卡羅來納州)|希爾頓黑德島]]<ref name="disney">{{cite web |url=https://twitter.com/SterlingKnight/status/7380774790 |title=Sterling Knight Twitter |work=Twitter |accessdate=2013-07-01 |archive-date=2013-12-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131203055359/https://twitter.com/SterlingKnight/status/7380774790 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他有一個姊妹Samantha Scarlett和一個兄弟Spencer Shuga<ref name="ktla">{{Cite video | people = Rubin, Sam (entertainment reporter, interviewer); Sterling Knight; Michaela Pereira | date = 2010-02-12 | title = KTLA Morning News | url = <!--Omitted - It was a "Sterling Knight Interview StarStruck" located on YouTube--> | publisher=[[KTLA|KTLA]] | location = Los Angeles | accessdate = March 12, 2010 | time = 1:30 | quote = [Pereira:] What is your sister's name? [Knight:] Samantha Scarlett. [Pereira:] And your brother? [Knight:] Spencer Shuga… My mom is a Georgia Girl. [Rubin:] Do you have a rap middle name too? [Knight:] I, umm, it's pretty bad. Sandmann. I'm not kidding… I will show you my ID…}}</ref>。

